[IMG]http://i856.photobucket.com/albums/ab122/kryptixsigs/GHKdR.gif[/img] Website: [url=http://tannerrsc.3owl.com]TannerRSC[/url] V2 has been released, client download [url=http://tannerrsc.3owl.com]Here[/url]. The server is now up for testing. [b][u]Latest News:[/u][/b]
Today I've finished highscores for the EasyRSC server. preview: [img]http://i856.photobucket.com/albums/ab122/kryptixsigs/hiscores.png[/img]
